title: BRIEF-Pacific Smiles Group Says HY Undelying ‍Net Profit Attributable $4.9 Mln

organizations.name: brief-pacific smiles group says hy undelying ‍net profit attributable

text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Pacific Smiles Group Ltd:
* HY UNDELYING ‍NET PROFIT ATTRIBUTABLE TO MEMBERS $4.9 MILLION VERSUS $5.4 MILLION
* ‍HY UNDERLYING REVENUE FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES $50.5 MILLION, UP 10.8%​
* ‍FY 2018 INTERIM DIVIDEND 2.30 CPS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
